query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('asp-classic',
'data-binding',
'e-commerce',
'eclipselink',
'facebook-like',
'ffmpeg',
'jboss',
'microsoft-edge',
'mkmapview',
'rust',
'ssrs-2008',
'stack-overflow',
'telerik',
'windows-phone-8');
